<OrgName><entry>INTEGRATED TERMINATION OF PREGNANCY SERVICE</entry>
</OrgName>
<Desc><entry>Integrated service between NHS Sheffield and Sheffield Teaching Hospitals NHS Trust.  Arranges termination of pregnancy on referral from GPs, family planning clinics or other agencies.  Service offers medical termination to 18 weeks pregnant, surgical termination to 12 weeks pregnant and local anaesthetic termination to 8 weeks pregnant.  Hospital beds are at the Royal Hallamshire Hospital.  Counselling can be arranged pre and post termination if required.</entry>
</Desc>
